OL,3,CMan guilty of targeting five women on
OL,4,Cone morning in town centre
OL,6,FA Tunisian man has been convicted of a
OL,7,Fspate of offences after randomly
OL,8,Ftargeting five women on one morning in
OL,9,FSt Helier town centre.
OL,11,FIt took the jury at Jersey's Royal
OL,12,FCourt just four hours to find
OL,13,FAbdelkarim Arfaoui, 27, guilty on all
OL,14,F10 counts - including attempted rape,
OL,15,Fsexual touching, grave and criminal
OL,16,Fassault, common assault, and
OL,17,Fthreatening or abusive behaviour.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
