PN,35702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784918934
OL,3,CMan guilty of targeting five women on
OL,4,Cone morning in town centre
OL,6,FThe jury saw CCTV footage showing
OL,7,FArfaoui make multiple approaches to
OL,8,Fvarious women between 6am and 7:30am
OL,9,Fon Sunday 30 November 2025.
OL,11,FThe defendant had been out the night
OL,12,Fbefore to celebrate receiving his
OL,13,Ffirst wage from a new job, having
OL,14,Farrived in Jersey last summer to live
OL,15,Fwith his wife.
OL,17,FThe States of Jersey Police were first
OL,18,Fcalled just after 7am when a woman
OL,19,Freported being sexually assaulted and
OL,20,Fpunched in the face while walking to
OL,21,Fwork.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784918934
OL,3,CMan guilty of targeting five women on
OL,4,Cone morning in town centre
OL,6,FA second report was received inside 20
OL,7,Fminutes from another woman who also
OL,8,Ftold them she had been sexually
OL,9,Fassaulted on her way to her job.
OL,11,FEight minutes after this report,
OL,12,FArfaoui was arrested - with three
OL,13,Ffurther victims later identified.
OL,15,FThe force has welcomed the guilty
OL,16,Fverdict and stressed that the Island's
OL,17,Fstreets are safe.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
