PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784918934
OL,3,CMan guilty of targeting five women on
OL,4,Cone morning in town centre
OL,6,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,7,FConstable Jack Maguire, adds:
OL,8,F"Offending of this nature is rare and
OL,9,Fthe States of Jersey Police, alongside
OL,10,Four partner agencies, are committed to
OL,11,Frobustly investigating offenders and
OL,12,Fbringing them to justice.
OL,14,F"Today's verdict is a testament to the
OL,15,Fbravery and courage of the five women
OL,16,Fwho came forward and supported this
OL,17,Finvestigation. It is because of their
OL,18,Fevidence that a dangerous sexual
OL,19,Fpredator has been convicted.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
