OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784918934
OL,3,CMan guilty of targeting five women on
OL,4,Cone morning in town centre
OL,6,F"Several key witnesses were identified
OL,7,Ffollowing public appeals through the
OL,8,Fmedia and social media, and extensive
OL,9,Fhouse-to-house enquiries carried out
OL,10,Fin the days after the offences.
OL,12,F"Their assistance played an important
OL,13,Frole in helping us build the evidence
OL,14,Fpresented before the court."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
